{"id":981,"date":"2017-12-22T07:57:25","date_gmt":"2017-12-22T07:57:25","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/byzan.vn\/?p=981"},"modified":"2021-02-27T09:46:46","modified_gmt":"2021-02-27T09:46:46","slug":"hieu-ung-anh-sang-trong-thiet-ke-noi-hien-dai","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/hieu-ung-anh-sang-trong-thiet-ke-noi-hien-dai\/","title":{"rendered":"Hi\u1ec7u \u1ee9ng \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng trong thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i"},"content":{"rendered":"<p><span style=\"font-family: 'times new roman', times, serif; font-size: 14pt;\">&nbsp;<em>\u00c1nh s\u00e1ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi\u1ebfu trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t, &nbsp;\u00e1nh s\u00e1ng l\u00e0 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 thu h\u00fat m\u1ecdi \u00e1nh nh\u00ecn v\u00e0 g\u00f3p ph\u1ea7n t\u1ea1o n\u00ean kh\u00f4ng gian s\u1ed1ng tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i. \u0110i\u1ec1u c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft \u0111\u1eb7t ra cho \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 t\u1ea1o ra s\u1ef1 d\u1ec5 ch\u1ecbu, th\u01b0 gi\u00e3n.<\/em><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 'times new roman', times, serif; font-size: 14pt;\">\u00c1nh s\u00e1ng trong thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i c\u1ea7n c\u00f3 ba y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 sau:<\/span><\/p>\n<ol>\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 'times new roman', times, serif;\">\u00c1nh s\u00e1ng t\u1ed5ng th\u1ec3<\/span><\/strong><\/span><\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 'times new roman', times, serif; font-size: 14pt;\">\u00c1nh s\u00e1ng t\u1ed5ng th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 c\u1ea5p \u0111\u1ed9 \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ea7n ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ebfn khi thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t. N\u00f3 bao g\u1ed3m \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng chung&nbsp; cho to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 ng\u1ed9i nh\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1eb7t tr\u00ean tr\u1ea7n ho\u1eb7c \u1edf gi\u1eefa ph\u00f2ng nh\u01b0: \u0111\u00e8n ch\u00f9m, \u0111\u00e8n tr\u1ea7n, \u0111\u00e8n treo t\u01b0\u1eddng; \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng t\u1ef1 nhi\u00ean. \u00c1nh s\u00e1ng t\u1ed5ng th\u1ec3 ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 ngu\u1ed3n s\u00e1ng ch\u00ednh cho c\u0103n h\u1ed9, khi s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng c\u00e1c lo\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e8n kh\u00e1c nhau s\u1ebd t\u1ea1o ra c\u00e1c hi\u1ec7u \u1ee9ng \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng kh\u00e1c nhau tuy nhi\u00ean m\u1ee5c \u0111\u00edch c\u1ee7a \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng n\u00e0y l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n c\u1ee5 th\u1ec3 trong m\u1ed9t c\u0103n ph\u00f2ng hay c\u0103n h\u1ed9.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-989\" src=\"http:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/khach-bep-view2-1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1800\" height=\"900\" srcset=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/khach-bep-view2-1.jpg 1800w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/khach-bep-view2-1-300x150.jpg 300w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/khach-bep-view2-1-1024x512.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/khach-bep-view2-1-768x384.jpg 768w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/khach-bep-view2-1-1536x768.jpg 1536w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1800px) 100vw, 1800px\" \/><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 'times new roman', times, serif; font-size: 14pt;\">V\u00ed d\u1ee5 ph\u00f2ng kh\u00e1ch l\u00e0 n\u01a1i c\u1ea7n \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng chung v\u00ec c\u0103n ph\u00f2ng n\u00e0y l\u00e0 n\u01a1i m\u1ecdi th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean trong gia \u0111\u00ecnh t\u1eadp trung. \u00c1nh s\u00e1ng th\u00edch h\u1ee3p c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0m c\u1ea3 gia \u0111\u00ecnh th\u01b0 gi\u00e3n, ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i. Ch\u00fang ta c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfc \u0111\u00e8n c\u00e2y \u1edf b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh sofa. S\u1ef1 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p c\u1ee7a hai lo\u1ea1i \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng s\u1ebd mang l\u1ea1i \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t cho thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-975\" src=\"http:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/Thiet-ke-can-ho-du-an-chi-yen-fivestar-2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1400\" height=\"980\"><\/span><\/p>\n<ol start=\"2\">\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 'times new roman', times, serif;\">\u00c1nh s\u00e1ng t\u1eadp trung<\/span><\/strong><\/span><\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 'times new roman', times, serif; font-size: 14pt;\">\u00c1nh s\u00e1ng t\u1eadp trung \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng nhi\u1ec1u trong ph\u00f2ng b\u1ebfp, ph\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ecdc s\u00e1ch,\u2026 M\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 lo\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e8n chi\u1ebfu cho \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng n\u00e0y: \u0111\u00e8n b\u00e0n, s\u00e0n, \u0111\u00e8n t\u1ee7 chi\u1ebfu,\u2026. \u0110\u1eb7c \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng lo\u1ea1i \u0111\u00e8n tr\u00ean l\u00e0 \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c gi\u1ea3m \u0111\u1ed9 r\u1ed9ng chi\u1ebfu s\u00e1ng, \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1eadp trung \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o n\u00ean hi\u1ec7u \u1ee9ng ri\u00eang cho m\u1ed9t khu v\u1ef1c.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-993\" src=\"http:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/ngu-ong-ba-view1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1773\" height=\"1050\" srcset=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/ngu-ong-ba-view1.jpg 1773w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/ngu-ong-ba-view1-300x178.jpg 300w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/ngu-ong-ba-view1-768x455.jpg 768w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/ngu-ong-ba-view1-1024x606.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1773px) 100vw, 1773px\" \/><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 'times new roman', times, serif; font-size: 14pt;\">\u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ee7, n\u00ean s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng v\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 c\u0103n ph\u00f2ng \u1ea5m \u00e1p h\u01a1n v\u00e0 t\u1ea1o c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c d\u1ec5 ch\u1ecbu cho \u0111\u00f4i m\u1eaft. \u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u00edch \u0111\u1ecdc s\u00e1ch tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111i ng\u1ee7 h\u00e3y l\u1eafp th\u00eam m\u1ed9t \u0111\u00e8n \u0111\u1ecdc s\u00e1ch \u1ed1p \u0111\u1ea7u gi\u01b0\u1eddng ho\u1eb7c \u0111\u00e8n b\u00e0n \u1edf tasb \u0111\u1ea7u gi\u01b0\u1eddng.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-991\" src=\"http:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/khach-bep-view5.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1800\" height=\"1100\" srcset=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/khach-bep-view5.jpg 1800w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/khach-bep-view5-300x183.jpg 300w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/khach-bep-view5-768x469.jpg 768w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/khach-bep-view5-1024x626.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1800px) 100vw, 1800px\" \/><\/span><\/p>\n<ol start=\"3\">\n<li><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\"><strong><span style=\"font-family: 'times new roman', times, serif;\">\u00c1nh s\u00e1ng trang tr\u00ed<\/span><\/strong><\/span><\/li>\n<\/ol>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 'times new roman', times, serif; font-size: 14pt;\">\u00c1nh s\u00e1ng trang tr\u00ed hay c\u00f2n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c g\u1ecdi l\u00e0 \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng tr\u1ecdng t\u00e2m, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 lo\u1ea1i \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng d\u00f9ng cho vi\u1ec7c trang tr\u00ed h\u01a1n l\u00e0 ch\u1ee9c n\u0103ng chi\u1ebfu s\u00e1ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-928\" src=\"http:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/Thiet-ke-du-an-vinhome-gardenia-6.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"1600\" height=\"1200\"><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 'times new roman', times, serif; font-size: 14pt;\">\u00c1nh s\u00e1ng tr\u1ecdng t\u00e2m gi\u00fap thu h\u00fat s\u1ef1 ch\u00fa \u00fd v\u00e0o \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n c\u1ee7a c\u0103n ph\u00f2ng v\u00e0 l\u00e0m n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt ch\u00fang. \u0110\u1ec3 l\u00e0m c\u0103n ph\u00f2ng tr\u00f4ng c\u00f3 v\u1ebb r\u1ed9ng r\u00e3i v\u00e0 cao h\u01a1n, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111\u1eb7t b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e8n d\u1ecdc theo b\u1ee9c t\u01b0\u1eddng, \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u00e8n s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c tr\u1ea3i t\u1eeb tr\u00ean&nbsp; xu\u1ed1ng d\u01b0\u1edbi. \u0110\u1ec3 t\u1ed1i \u0111a \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng trong thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n \u0111\u1ea1i, b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u00eam m\u1ed9t v\u00e0i t\u1ea5m g\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u1ea3n chi\u1ebfu \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng, khi\u1ebfn c\u0103n ph\u00f2ng c\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c r\u1ed9ng h\u01a1n, \u0111\u1eb9p v\u00e0 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng.<\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 14pt;\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-890\" src=\"http:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/IMG_9985.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"5472\" height=\"3648\" srcset=\"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/IMG_9985.jpg 5472w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/IMG_9985-300x200.jpg 300w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/IMG_9985-768x512.jpg 768w, https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-content\/uploads\/2017\/12\/IMG_9985-1024x683.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 5472px) 100vw, 5472px\" \/><\/span><\/p>\n<p><span style=\"font-family: 'times new roman', times, serif; font-size: 14pt;\">\u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi ph\u00f2ng kh\u00e1ch n\u00ean 20-25m c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u00e8n chi\u1ebfu s\u00e1ng chung v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o r\u1eb1ng c\u0103n ph\u00f2ng kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 qu\u00e1 3 \u0111\u00e8n chi\u1ebfu c\u1ee5 b\u1ed9. \u0110\u00e8n \u0111\u1ec3 trang tr\u00ed n\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1ea9n v\u00ec \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang th\u01b0\u1eddng h\u01a1i ch\u00f3i.<\/span><\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>&nbsp;\u00c1nh s\u00e1ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 thi\u1ebfu trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh thi\u1ebft k\u1ebf n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t, &nbsp;\u00e1nh s\u00e1ng l\u00e0 y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 thu h\u00fat m\u1ecdi \u00e1nh nh\u00ecn v\u00e0 g\u00f3p ph\u1ea7n t\u1ea1o n\u00ean kh\u00f4ng gian s\u1ed1ng tho\u1ea3i m\u00e1i. \u0110i\u1ec1u c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft \u0111\u1eb7t ra cho \u00e1nh s\u00e1ng \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 t\u1ea1o ra s\u1ef1 d\u1ec5 ch\u1ecbu, th\u01b0 gi\u00e3n. \u00c1nh&#8230;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":989,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[154],"tags":[],"class_list":["post-981","post","type-post","status-publish","format-standard","has-post-thumbnail","hentry","category-chia-se-kien-thuc"],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/981","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=981"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/981\/revisions"}],"wp:featuredmedia":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media\/989"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=981"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/byzan.vn\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=98